inventory |
| `netbox_ceph` | [`emersonfelipesp/netbox-ceph`] | Read-only
Proxmox-managed Ceph inventory |
| `netbox_pdm` | [`emersonfelipesp/netbox-pdm`] | Proxmox Datacenter
Manager inventory |
| `netbox_packer` | [`emersonfelipesp/netbox-packer`] | HashiCorp Packer
image-factory for Proxmox |

## What's New in v0.0.18

Paired with backend [`proxbox-api 0.0.14`].

- **Full PVE 9.2 support.** New models for SDN fabrics, route maps, prefix
lists, and custom datacenter CPU models, plus automated sync services.
Completed per-node firewall sync. HA arm/disarm action views.
`ProxmoxNode.location` field.

Full notes: [Release Notes — v0.0.18].

