## Requirements

- NetBox 4.5.8, 4.5.9, or 4.6.x
- Verified with NetBox v4.5.8, v4.5.9, v4.6.0, and official v4.6.1
- Python 3.12+
- Proxmox VE 7.x, 8.x, or 9.x (PVE 9 requires `VM.GuestAgent.Audit` on the
API role; see "Troubleshooting" below for the PVE 9 auth checklist)


